    public abstract class TickingTankInventoryTileEntity<T extends TankInventoryTileEntity>
extends TankInventoryTileEntity
implements org.cyclops.cyclopscore.tileentity.CyclopsTileEntity.ITickingTile
    A TileEntity with Tank and Inventory that can tick. It uses a list of TickComponent that are able to tick. And these components will contain a collection of ITickAction that can perform specific actions depending on the condition of the TickComponent.
    See Also:
    TickComponent
